{"id": "art-1071", "label": "Art. 1071", "title": "Art. 1071", "slug": "art-1071", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_461445059\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2348\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_461445059\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 107<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1589360188\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2347\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1589360188\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Subscrierea, dobândirea sau <span class=SpellE>de&#355;inerea</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> ale unei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> de c&#259;tre o alt&#259; societate\nla care societatea pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;ine</span>, direct sau indirect, majoritatea drepturilor\nde vot sau ale c&#259;rei decizii pot fi <span class=SpellE>influen&#355;ate</span>\nîn mod semnificativ de societatea pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\neste considerat&#259; ca fiind efectuat&#259; de c&#259;tre societatea pe <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> <span class=SpellE>îns&#259;&#351;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_81630539\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2346\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_81630539\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span> alin. (1) se\nvor aplica <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> atunci când societatea prin\nintermediul c&#259;reia se efectueaz&#259; subscrierea, dobândirea sau <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;inerea</span> de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;ionat&#259;</span> este guvernat&#259; de <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legea</i> unui alt stat.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}